title: Obama focusing on condolences, not gun laws, in Oregon visit
text: > Top News Obama focusing on condolences, not gun laws, in Oregon visit President Barack Obama boards Marine One for the short flight to Roseburg, Ore. following his arrival on Air Force One in Eugene, Ore., Friday, Oct. 9, 2015. Obama is traveling to Roseburg, Ore., to meet with families of the victims of the Oct. 1, shooting at Umpqua Community College, as part of a four-day West Coast tour. Obama is also scheduled to attend a fundraiser event later today in Seattle with Sen. Patty Murray, D-Wash. He's is also attending fundraisers in San Francisco and Los Angeles during the four-day visit. (AP Photo/Pablo Martinez Monsivais)
